# MOBILE DESIGN

Generate a fully responsive mobile version matching the provided design.

Requirements:

* Hamburger menu
* Stacked cards
* Responsive image grids
* Touch-friendly buttons
* Mobile service carousel
* Optimized spacing

Breakpoints:

* Mobile: 320px–767px
* Tablet: 768px–1024px
* Desktop: 1025px+

---

# UX REQUIREMENTS

Improve conversion rate by adding:

* Sticky CTA button
* Floating call button
* Quick quote form
* Service booking modal
* Customer trust badges
* Satisfaction guarantee badge
* Emergency service badge

---

# ACCESSIBILITY

Must satisfy WCAG AA.

Requirements:

* Semantic HTML
* Keyboard navigation
* Focus states
* Proper ARIA labels
* Color contrast compliance
* Screen reader support

---

# ANIMATIONS

Use subtle Material Design motion:

* Card hover elevation
* Fade-in sections
* Smooth scrolling
* Button ripple effects
* Micro-interactions

No excessive animations.

---

# SEO

Include:

* Meta title
* Meta description
* Open Graph tags
* Structured data
* Local business schema

Target keywords:

* Home Cleaning Services
* Deep Cleaning
* Move Out Cleaning
* Office Cleaning
* House Cleaning Near Me

---

# DELIVERABLES

Generate:

1. Complete UX Architecture
2. Sitemap
3. User Flow
4. Wireframe Description
5. Design System
6. Full Responsive UI Specification
7. Production Ready HTML
8. Production Ready SCSS
9. Production Ready JavaScript
10. Accessibility Report
11. SEO Recommendations

The generated result should closely match the uploaded Figma design while maintaining modern Material Design aesthetics and professional home-services branding.
